message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this excellent product. I think it would be incredibly beneficial for you. Given its value, I'm proposing a starting price of $14,000. What do you think?

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I believe I can find a better deal elsewhere. I am willing to pay up to $10,000 for the product. Let me know if this is something you can consider.
